{"text_id":121738,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," utilize"," gamma","-","ray"," observations"," to"," probe"," the"," cosmic","-","ray"," pressure"," in"," galaxy"," clusters"," and"," its"," cosmological"," implications","."," The"," motivation"," behind"," this"," research"," is"," the"," possibility"," that"," cosmic"," rays",","," a"," significant"," component"," of"," the"," intra","cluster"," medium",","," could"," play"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," the"," dynamics"," and"," evolution"," of"," galaxy"," clusters","."," However",","," cosmic"," rays"," are"," not"," directly"," observable",","," and"," their"," pressure"," must"," be"," inferred"," indirectly"," through"," gamma","-","ray"," emission"," resulting"," from"," cosmic","-","ray"," interactions"," with"," cluster"," gas",".","\n\n","The"," key"," ideas"," of"," our"," work"," revolve"," around"," developing"," a"," methodology"," to"," estimate"," the"," cosmic","-","ray"," pressure"," using"," gamma","-","ray"," observations"," and"," applying"," this"," methodology"," to"," a"," sample"," of"," galaxy"," clusters","."," Our"," approach"," involves"," modeling"," gamma","-","ray"," emission"," from"," cosmic","-","ray"," protons",","," accounting"," for"," uncertainties"," in"," cosmic","-","ray"," spectra"," and"," spatial"," distribution","."," By"," comparing"," model"," predictions"," with"," gamma","-","ray"," observations",","," we"," infer"," the"," cosmic","-","ray"," pressure"," and"," investigate"," its"," relationship"," with"," other"," cluster"," properties",".","\n\n","The"," problem"," our"," work"," attempts"," to"," solve"," is"," understanding"," the"," role"," of"," cosmic"," rays"," in"," galaxy"," clusters"," and"," their"," impact"," on"," cosmological"," scales","."," Our"," results"," reveal"," a"," significant"," correlation"," between"," cosmic","-","ray"," pressure"," and"," the"," thermal"," pressure"," of"," the"," intra","cluster"," medium",","," suggesting"," a"," coupling"," between"," the"," two"," components","."," Furthermore",","," we"," find"," that"," cosmic"," rays"," could"," contribute"," significantly"," to"," the"," total"," pressure"," of"," galaxy"," clusters"," and"," the"," overall"," energy"," budget"," of"," the"," universe","."," These"," findings"," have"," important"," implications"," for"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," formation"," and"," evolution"," of"," large","-","scale"," structures"," in"," the"," universe",","," as"," well"," as"," the"," role"," of"," non","-","thermal"," components"," in"," the"," intra","cluster"," medium","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}